Package com.genologics.ri.sample

Class Summary
ArtifactLink Artifact is a child element of Sample and provides a URI linking to the detailed representation of the artifact for the Sample.
BioSource Deprecated. Biosource is not supported in Clarity.
ControlTypeLink Control Type provides a name and a URI linking to the detailed representation of the Control Type associated with the Sample.
ObjectFactory This object contains factory methods for each Java content interface and Java element interface generated in the com.genologics.ri.sample package.
ProjectLink Project is a child element of Sample and provides a URI linking to the detailed representation of the Project for the Sample.
Sample The detailed representation of a sample.
SampleBase The base representation of a Sample, defining common elements for both Sample and Sample creation.
SampleBatchFetchResult Batch fetch and update holder for samples.
SampleCreation Sample creation is the detailed representation required when creating a new Sample in the system.
SampleLink Sample-link is a child element type of samples and provides a URI linking to the detailed representation of a sample.
Samples The representation for a list of sample links.
Submitter Submitter is a child element of Sample and provides a URI linking to the detailed representation of the submitter for the Sample.
